quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,92,"On keЙ“ataa moЖґЖґere nden haa wiЕ‹toЙ—on e ko Й“uruЙ—on yiЙ—ude kon. Kala woo ko wiЕ‹tiЙ—on, pellet Alla no Anndi Й—um"
  3,93,"Kalo Г±amri laatino koko daganii Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila en, si wonaa ko Israa'iila harminanno hoore-mun ko adii Tawreeta Jippaade. Maaku: "ngaddee Tawreetaare nden jnanngon nde, si on laatiima gooЕ‹guЙ“e"."
  3,94,"Kala pekindiiЙ—o fenaande [dammbi] e Alla Й“aawo Й—um, ko Й“en Й—on woni tooГ±ooЙ“e Й“en."
  3,95,"Maaku: "Alla gooЕ‹Й—ii. Njokke diina Ibraahiima kan; ooГ±iika [gaa diinaaji mehre], o laatanooki jeyaaЙ—o e Й“en sirkooЙ“e."
  3,96,"Pellet, aranndu e Suudu waЙ—anaandu yimЙ“e Й“en, ko ndun wondu Bakkata; barkinaandu e peewal wonan de Winndere nden."
  3,97,"Ino e mayru kaawisaaji Й“annguЙ—e : darorde Ibraahiima nden. Kala naatuЙ—o e mayru, o laatoo kooliiЙ—o. No woodani Alla e dow yimЙ“e Й“en hajjugol ka Suudu [hormaandu], wona nde on hattanЙ—o e mayru laawol. Kala on yedduЙ—o, pellet, Alla ko YonndiniiЙ—o e winndere nden."
  3,98,"Maaku: "Hey mon yimЙ“e Defte, e ko njeddanton Aayeeje Alla Й—iin, Alla ko ceediiЙ—o ko ngolloton kon?"."
  3,99,"Maaku: "Hey mon yimЙ“e Defte, ko falotoЙ—on e laawol Alla ngol, on gomЙ—inЙ—o HoЙ—on Й—aЙ“Й“ana ngol ooГ±anЙ—e tara ko on seediiЙ“e! Alla wonaali WelsindiiЙ—o e ko ngolloton kon"."
  3,100,"Hey mon gooЕ‹Й—inЙ“e, si on Й—oftike fedde e Й“en okkaaЙ“e defte, Й“e nduttay on heeferЙ“e Й“aawo gooЕ‹Й—inal mon."